text.tspan: This certification adds or replaces options
given in the Basic Rifleman Kit.
No supressors on M75 or M739.
No use of AP rounds in M33-T.

tspan.tspan: Autorifle boxes are heavy and bulky. Take the extra time to
"inventory tetris" your bag to maximize your carrying capacity.
Remember: you must still carry minimum medical and other

text.tspan: essential supplies given in the Basic Rifleman Kit.

tspan.tspan: Specializing in support by fire and suppression of enemy forces through
volume of fire, the Autorifleman wields a mobile light machine gun (LMG)
and a sizable reserve of ammunition to ensure that both the enemy's

text.tspan: bodies and their teammates' eardrums are heavily perforated.
